title: Remix Artist Collective (RAC) - Chapter One
description:
RAC's Album Chapter One, with fresh remixes from Two Door Cinema Club, Foster The People, Phoenix, and others.

1. Something Good Can Work (Two Door Cinema Club)
2. Houdini (Foster The People)
3. Armistice (Phoenix)
4. Everything You Wanted (Kele)
5. Sweet Disposition (The Temper Trap)
6. Sleeping Lessons (The Shins)
7. Home (Edward Sharpe & The Magnetic Zeros)
8. New Theory (Washed Out)
9. Why Even Try (Theophilus London)
10. When I'm Small (Phantogram)
11. No Strings (Mayor Hawthorne)
12. Wait Up (Tokyo Police Club)
13. Bonafied Lovin (Chromeo)
14. Boy (Ra Ra Riot)
15. The Worse It Gets (Penguin Prison)
16. Stranger Love (Classixx)
17. Back in Your Head (Tegan and Sara)
18. Concrete Wall (Zee Avi)
19. Blue Jeans (Lana Del Rey)
20. RAC Radio (RAC)

All songs are encoded at 320kbps, with a 1600x1600 embedded cover image. Nothing extraneous; only quality.
